name: Introducing Danika Smith EP
description: Danika Smith is a young Singer Songwriter from the Far North Coast of NSW. She recently featured on Triple J Unearthed High with two songs, 'Oh Father" and "You Matter to Me". She received a significant amount of interest and air play, becoming one of the six finalists in that competition. She continues to write and takes every opportunity to perform live. This Introductory EP includes those known songs plus two new ones, "Shallow" and "Man on the Moon", and an earlier one "It's Not Me, It's Not You". For those who have come to know Danika's music, and who have been waiting to purchase her CD -  now, with the generous assistance and expertise of her musical mentors - Here it is!! Enjoy.
